data.description: If you're looking for a home in North East, look no further! This gorgeous and one of a kind 2500+ square foot home also comes with a massive 3600+ square foot detached garage! This well taken care of home offers 4 large bedrooms, newer flooring throughout, multiple living areas and a back deck which is perfect for entertaining or hosting! All while being just a short walk away from downtown North East and all its amenities! Call today!
